Description_lang: Tectus is unkillable as long as he is under the affects of The Living Mountain.He will periodically gain energy, with the rate of gain increasing as he loses health.The power of The Living Mountain is consumed whenever Tectus channels Tectonic Upheaval, leaving him vulnerable to shattering.
AuraDescription_lang: Unkillable.Applies Accretion to himself and nearby Fragments of Tectus every $t1 sec.
